      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DEADLY GRIN (1) is in top form notching back to back wins, the latest over 340m in (19.49) at this track. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in two starts. Great chance again. CANYA LEXI (2) comes here after a good win at this track over 461m in 25.97. This tougher but looks a leading chance again. BLAND OPTION (3) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing eighth (25.87) in a Grade 5 at Sale. Goes very well at the trip finding the frame in each of four starts. Better than last start and can bounce back. CABAO KYANITE (8) was below best last time at this track (19.92) in a Grade 4, finishing a 8 length eighth. Has two wins already from this draw.",
